<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.4.6">
<l>pūtamaintoṭu vēḷviyaintupu laṉkaḷaintupo ṟikaḷāl</l>
<l>ētamoṉṟumi lātavaṇkaiyi ṉārkaḷvāḻtiruk kōṭṭiyūr</l>
<l>nātaṉainara ciṅkaṉainaviṉ ṟēttuvārkaḷu ḻakkiya</l>
<l>pātatūḷipa ṭutalālivu lakampākkiyañ ceytatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirukkōṭṭiyūr dwell those with generous hands,</l>
<l rend="indent">without a single flaw [occuring] with the five elements,</l>
<l rend="indent">five sacrifices, five senses, and five sense organs,</l>
<l>this earth experiences the fortune of bearing the dust</l>
<l rend="indent">on the feet that is stirred up by those who praise,</l>
<l rend="indent">saying “Nātha!” “Narasiṃha!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
